Usage: reset_timing_derate [-help] [<object_list>]
                           [-delay_corner <delayCornerName>] [-increment]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>                       # Specifies the list of cells, nets, or
                                    # library cells to reset (string, optional)
-delay_corner <delayCornerName>     # Specifies the list of delay corners on
                                    # which reset derating is to be applied
                                    # (string, optional)
-increment                          # reset the incremental derates applied in
                                    # all (OCV/AOCV/SOCV) mode. (bool, optional)